casebody.data:
James D. DONOVAN, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
ESTATE OF Patricia H. DONOVAN File No. 2016 CP 4798 NC, Kendry Oyen, Estate of Timothy J. Dovovan, Patricia H. Donovan Revocable Trust Dated September 6, 1984, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3522 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 25, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This appeal is dismissed for lack of jurisdiction. Appellant's resubmitted motion for review of order denying motion to stay is denied as moot.

KELLY, VILLANTI, and MORRIS, JJ., Concur.
